            "section": "A febrile patient with sepsis induced MODS and features of macrophage activation syndrome"
        },
        {
            "text": "Clinical history and presentation with new onset hyperferritinemia help the intensivist to recognize uncontrolled inflammation and need for subspecialty consultation. Determination of the best treatment approaches for these patients is in need of clinical trial evaluation. ",
